pr_title: [GSoC Milestone 1] Migrate resource calls from RESTEasy to GitLab4J-API
pr_body:
This PR migrates the GitLab Plugin's resource calls from RESTEasy to GitLab4J-API without affecting the older Webhook implementation. The Proxy Configuration is currently non-functional.

An attempt has been made to adapt Docker Based Functional Tests accordingly.

pr_body:
Migrating the old manual Webhook implementation to GitLab4J-API event-based Webhook.
This PR is based on Milestone 1 code.
CauseData has been fixed. It wont be broken according to events.
MergeRequest has issue of `auto-merge`.
Tests not completely adapted yet.
